item.title: Need help with JDK 6.0 download
item.dc:creator: @A.E.M A.E.M.
item.description:
@A.E.M wrote:

right click on your compile.bat and click edit and enter this code

[code]@echo off
COLOR 0a

Java Compiler
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_02\bin\javac.exe” *.java
pause
[/code]
